For Croogo 1.3.1

Install:
- Put the flattr folder in your app/plugins directory or upload this plugin as a zip in your admin menu
- Enter your Flattr uid in config/flattr.php
- optionally change the other settings
- activate the helper hook in your admin menu

The Flattr Helper (flattr/views/helpers/flattr.php):
I first coded the FlattrHelper as standalone helper. It still can be used as such and therefore has a lot of comments in it.
So if you are curious, you can read the whole thing. ;)